E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('915','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;本以为至少要花七八千元，没想到最后一算账才<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3200</span>元，减去能在新农合报销<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2600</span>多元，自己只需出<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500</span>多元。&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">21</span>日，长期患有高血压、肺气肿、气管炎的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">73</span>岁朱大爷，说起洲湾镇卫生院实行药品&ldquo;零差价&rdquo;的惠民政策，感激之情溢于言表。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">朱大爷去年在镇卫生院住了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>多天院，共用去医药费<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7500</span>多元。而今年在相同医院住院，用的药与去年差不多，因为实行了药品&ldquo;零差价&rdquo;，药费却少了一半多。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据了解，从<st1:chsdate isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"26\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2010\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2010</span>年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">26</span>日</st1:chsdate>开始，嘉鱼县全县<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>家镇卫生院、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>家社区中心、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>家村卫生室全部实施了国家基本药物制度，取消了药品加成销售，实行了零差率销售。同时，按照全省统一安排，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">484</span>种基本药物实行省级网上公开招标采购药品、统一配送。建立财政补偿机制，基本药物全部纳入基本医疗保险药品报销目录，做到真正&ldquo;还利于民&rdquo;。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">目前，全县基层医疗机构与去年同期相比，药品价格下降<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">49.125%</span>、药品与业务占比下降<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15%</span>左右，门急诊均次费用下降<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">31%</span>；门诊量同比增加<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25%</span>，受到群众欢迎。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">该县卫生局局长刘守锡介绍说：&ldquo;实施国家基本药物制度后，由于药品价格和住院费用的下降，加上新农合报销比例和范围进一步扩大，病人就诊费用明显减少，大大减轻了病人的经济负担，让患者得到更多实惠。&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>');");
