\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">全镇国土面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">173</span>平方公里，辖<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13</span>个村民委员会、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>个社区，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">99</span>个村民小组，总人口<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3.7</span>万人。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2010</span>年全镇实现社会总产值<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">31.31</span>亿元，其中工业产值<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">28.21</span>亿元，农业产值<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3.1</span>亿元；实现规模以上工业增加值<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6.5</span>亿元；全社会固定资产投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7.6</span>亿元；招商引资到位资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3.6</span>亿元；农民人均纯收入达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6202</span>元，完成国地税收<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2742</span>万元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 5pt 0cm; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">这里有&ldquo;中国第一组&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">官桥八组；有国家级高新技术企业田野集团股份有限公司，占地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>平方公里，拥有嘉裕管业、长江合金、神农制药、中石特管等企业<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>家，总资产达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>亿元；有&ldquo;湖北螃蟹之乡&rdquo;最大螃蟹养殖场</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">西凉湖万亩围栏养蟹基地；有<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.2</span>万亩花卉苗木基地；有全省闻名的高标准设施农业科技示范园</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">湖北大禾现代农业基地；有部优名茶</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">凤凰舌尖；全镇油茶种植面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10000</span>多亩，茶叶面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13000</span>亩，水产面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50000</span>亩，形成了茶叶、蔬菜、水产、林果、油茶五大农业产业板块；建成了面积达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>平方公里的以森工产业为主，电子产业为辅的工业园，目前入园企业有恒鑫脚手架制造有限公司、迈悦科技有限公司、永强新型环保建筑材料有限公司等<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>家，投资总额<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">70</span>多亿元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 5pt 0cm; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">近年来，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">镇党委、政府紧紧围绕县委、县政府提出的建设&ldquo;农业强县、工业大县、旅游新县&rdquo;的战略目标，始终坚持解放思想，始终坚持科学发展，增强机遇意识、发展意识、责任意识，推进新型工业化、农业产业化、城乡一体化，建设&ldquo;工业强镇、农业新镇、旅游名镇&rdquo;，打造&ldquo;嘉鱼后花园，鄂南中心镇&rdquo;，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">先后被上级授予：全省乡镇（街道）纪检组织示范单位、咸宁市乡镇党委&ldquo;十面红旗&rdquo;、咸宁市文明乡镇、咸宁市&ldquo;百镇千村&rdquo;、&ldquo;清洁家园&rdquo;建设先进单位、全县食品安全工作先进单位、全县党风廉政建设责任制先进单位、全县&ldquo;万名干部进万村入万户&rdquo;活动先进单位、县&ldquo;五好&rdquo;镇党委等几十项荣誉称号。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 5pt 0cm; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>');");
