E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('926','283','嘉鱼政务网编辑','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"DSC04141_副本.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"500\\\\\" height=\\\\\"375\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xiangzhenlianjie/2011-11-25/efffdab5585a40f27f8683f3787aeea1.jpg\\\\\" /></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">新街镇西靠县城、南望赤壁、北滨长江，武蒲公路贯穿全镇，辖<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>个行政村，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>个居委会，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.72</span>万人。镇域版土面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">109</span>平方公里，耕地面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4.8</span>万亩，呈现&ldquo;一山三水六分田&rdquo;地域。交通便捷，区位极优，是嘉鱼县的蔬菜重镇，水产强镇，意杨大镇和甘蔗之乡，是远近闻名的鄂南特色农业镇。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">近年来，镇党委、政府以十六、十七大精神和科学发展观为指导，深化&ldquo;工业强镇、特色兴镇、环境美镇、和谐立镇、党建治镇&rdquo;五大战略，努力做好&ldquo;招商引资和特色农业&rdquo;两篇文章，实现了经济快速发展和社会各项事业的全面进步。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">新街镇农业资源丰富，经过多年的结构调整，明确&ldquo;沿路发展菜和瓜、沿江发展意杨林、沿湖发展鱼虾蟹、沿山发展果苗木&rdquo;的方向，</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">已形成万亩无公害大棚菜、万亩优质西甜瓜、万亩螃蟹养殖、万亩优质稻、万亩意杨、五千亩名优特水产养殖、五千亩红甘蔗、五千亩精细大棚等八大特色农业基地，全镇蔬菜种植面积达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>万亩，水产养殖面积达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>万亩。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2011</span>年进一步加大对特色农业的建设力度，投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>万元，在晒甲山新建蔬菜大棚<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>个，建设葡萄基地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">60</span>亩。还有近<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300</span>亩的设施农业正在洽谈之中。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">以全镇滨江邻城的区位优势，一级路、武汉城市外环高速、武深高速的交通优势，投资落户新街工业园的政策优势，倾力打造十里工业长廊，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2011</span>年投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3500</span>万元，拓展园区面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500</span>亩，达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1000</span>亩，引进了工业</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #333333; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''\\\\''\\\\\">企业<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>家，在建企业<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>家，签订了投资合同书并已预付征地平整资金的企业有<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">14</span>家，形成了落户一批、在建一批、在谈一批、储备一批的工业招商格局。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2011</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"color: #333333\\\\\">1-11</span><span style=\\\\\"color: #333333\\\\\">月份，</span>全镇工农业总产值达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">14</span>亿元，占全年计划的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>；国地两税收入入库达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1100</span>万元，占全年目标任务的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>；固定资产投资达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3.47</span>亿元，占全年计划的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">103%</span>；招商引资达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.36</span>亿元，占全年目标任务的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">130%</span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #333333; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''\\\\''\\\\\">。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">新街镇，是您观光休闲、旅游度假的好地方，更是您洽谈贸易、投资开发的理想去处。一握新街手，便成好朋友，新街人民热忱欢迎莅临新街，投资兴业。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('927','283','嘉鱼政务网编辑','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: center; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\"><img height=\\\\\"360\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"渡普镇政府3_副本.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"497\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xiangzhenlianjie/2011-11-24/5519fb9fa39e63ef82276849c566ee56.jpg\\\\\" /></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: justify; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\">渡普镇地处嘉鱼东大门，境内平原丘陵各半，濒临东、西两湖，是嘉鱼、赤壁、咸安、江夏四县市区水上交汇处，属古渡口，取&ldquo;渡普众生&rdquo;之意而得名，始建于清末民国初年，镇属烟墩为古三国东吴大都督鲁肃之故里。全镇版图面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">119</span>平方公里，咸潘公路穿镇而过，向西<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>公里是长江深水码头，向东<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>公里是京珠高速公路、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">107</span>国道和京广铁路，向北<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">65</span>公里是九省通衢的武汉市。全镇人口<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3.08</span>万人，集镇人口<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.2</span>万人，现辖<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>个行政村，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>个渔场，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>个居委会。耕地面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4.2</span>万亩，水域面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>万亩，是嘉鱼县的工业老镇、水产名镇、文化名镇。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: justify; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\">2010</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\">年，全镇共有规模以上企业<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>家，规模工业总产值<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7.7</span>亿元，实现了社会固定资产投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.2</span>亿元，招商引资到位资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8500</span>万元，财政收入<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">700</span>万元，新增城镇就业岗位<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">350</span>个，培训农民工达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">620</span>人。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: justify; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\">2010</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\">年，全镇农业总产值<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8.29</span>亿元，农民人均年收入达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6651</span>元。新修及硬化生产路<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>公里，沟渠清淤<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>公里，新修泵站<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>处，维修<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>处，并更新全部设备。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: justify; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\">2010</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\">年，全镇上下万众一心，战胜了特大洪涝灾害。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2011</span>年，镇党委、政府将借助长江大港区建设，核电一级路开工建设贯穿而过等发展良机，全面启动临港新城战略。全年将完成<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>万亩的土地平整，总投资达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9000</span>万元，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月份将完成东、西湖围堤维修建设，金水河综合治理工程年初开始动工，总投资达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1800</span>万元，另外，借助净宝农业发展公司，开展新农村建设，总投资达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3000</span>万元。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: justify; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\">渡普人民思想解放，勤劳勇敢，全镇上下注重体制和技术创新，<span style=\\\\\"letter-spacing: -1pt\\\\\">依托地方优势，不等不靠，积极争取各项政策支持，</span>坚持兴工强镇、兴农富民、维护稳定、科学发展。目前，烟墩<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500</span>亩工业园区已经动工兴建，欢迎各界仁人志士来渡普投资。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
